{"type": "article", "id": 19614, "title": "利用废弃塑料袋的家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-24T07:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122347tXHymYKu6kMbaRvA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t一根废弃塑料袋完全降解需要 1000 年的时间，不少设计师选择这种材料来设计新的东西。美国加州的设计师 Carter Zufelt 和团队一起用废弃的塑料袋做了一系列的文具，包括文具盒，笔筒、榖子、凳子等物品。依稀可以看到不同颜色的塑料袋的痕迹，很自然，有大理石云纹的感觉。产品正在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/83900559/mull-designer-objects-from-recycled-plastic-trash\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122344svGTz4wNnFgrbPm9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122345N3nfzZ0g5y2uXV7i.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122345GuVEr56g7W0hoDwn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122346ciEJkgXbT3oehSqH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122346VaRBpE5IiHwFCZOL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}